      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2). This example features the 3.6L flat-six M96 engine, recently enhanced with a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Air-Oil Separator (AOS) for long-term reliability. The G96 six-speed manual transaxle provides precise, short-throw engagement, distributing torque through the factory viscous-clutch AWD system. The chassis is anchored by Bilstein B6 dampers and factory-spec bushings, ensuring optimal kinematic response and surgical turn-in. Finished in Basalt Black Metallic with flawless paint depth and a pristine underside, this wide-body C4S is mechanically synchronized and cosmetically perfect.",
